  (text "SYSTEM: 16-Channel Electrometer / Picoammeter\nSignal Flow: J1 Input -> 16x Filters -> 2x MAX338 Mux -> ADA4530-1 TIA -> ADuCM362 ADC\nRange Selection: 4x Relay Ladder (10M/100M/1G/10G) driven by NPN transistors from MCU GPIO"
    (exclude_from_sim no)
    (at 50 30 0)
    (effects (font (size 2.54 2.54)) (justify left))
    (uuid "e0000001-0001-0001-0001-000000000001")
  )

  (text "NET LABEL KEY:\nCH_IN_1..16: Input channels from J1 triax connector\nMUX_A1..A8, MUX_B1..B8: Filtered signals to mux inputs\nTIA_IN: Mux output to TIA inverting input\nINV, OUT: TIA feedback nodes (relay ladder)\nAIN0: TIA output to MCU ADC\nAIN1: VREF monitor to MCU ADC\nADDR_A0..A2, EN_A, EN_B: Mux address and enable\nGP1_0..GP1_3: MCU GPIO to relay NPN drivers\nRELAY_0..RELAY_3: NPN collector to relay coils"
    (exclude_from_sim no)
    (at 50 60 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.524 1.524)) (justify left))
    (uuid "e0000002-0001-0001-0001-000000000001")
  )

)